      { "author": { "uri": { "label": "https://itunes.apple.com/gb/reviews/id1426120037" }, "name": { "label": "Isadorraavlive" }, "label": "" }, "updated": { "label": "2026-04-25T09:49:27-07:00" }, "im:rating": { "label": "5" }, "im:version": { "label": "10.125" }, "id": { "label": "13996060329" }, "title": { "label": "I would never change REVOLUT IS MY BANK FOREVER" }, "content": { "label": "If you’re still relying on traditional banks, it might be time to seriously reconsider. I’ve used Revolut across Personal, Pro, and Ultra accounts, and I’m even opening my business account with them—and the difference is on another level.\nWhat convinced me the most is the security and control. With Revolut, I actually feel like my money is protected. Everything is instant, transparent, and managed from the app. Features like real-time notifications, card controls, and advanced security give a level of confidence I never had with older banks.\nOn top of that, the flexibility is unmatched. Whether you’re managing daily spending, running side income through Pro, or preparing for a full business account, everything connects seamlessly. No delays, no unnecessary complications—just a system that works.\nTraditional banks often feel outdated, slow, and reactive. Revolut feels modern, fast, and built around the user. I haven’t had a single issue, and that consistency is exactly why I trust them with all my finances.\nFor anyone thinking about switching: it’s absolutely worth it. Once you experience the speed, security, and convenience, it’s very hard to go back.", "attributes": { "type": "text" } }, "link": { "attributes": { "rel": "related", "href": "https://itunes.apple.com/gb/review?id=932493382&type=Purple%20Software" } }, "im:voteSum": { "label": "0" }, "im:contentType": { "attributes": { "term": "Application", "label": "Application" } }, "im:voteCount": { "label": "0" } },
